Yawan masu kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) da ke karuwa cikin sauri a Tarayyar Turai da Burtaniya a tsakanin 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yawan kamuwa da cutar coronavirus (COVID-19) yana da irin wannan yanayin a cikin ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai da Burtaniya, don haka yana tabbatar da cewa duk da cewa akwai matakai daban-daban na ci gabanta a cikin ƙasashe daban-daban, annobar COVID-19 tana ƙaruwa cikin sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Bisa ga abin da Italiya ta yi, ƙasashe, asibitoci da dakunan jinya na musamman suna bukatar su kasance a shirye don karɓar masu cutar COVID-19 da ke buƙatar magani da kuma jinya mai tsanani.
A ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019, an sami wasu mutane da suka kamu da cutar sankarar bargo a birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 9 ga watan Janairun 2020, Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka ta kasar Sin ta sanar da cewa sabon nau'in coronavirus ne ya haifar da kamuwa da cutar, wanda yanzu aka sani da coronavirus mai fama da cutar cututtukan numfashi mai tsanani na 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Tun daga wannan lokacin, cutar da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa an kira ta cutar coronavirus (COVID-19).
A cewar bayanan da ake da su a yau, kusan kashi 80 cikin ɗari na mutanen da ke da COVID-19 suna da cutar mai sauƙi, wato, cutar numfashi tare da ciwon huhu ko a'a, kuma yawancin mutanen da ke fama da cutar suna murmurewa.
Kimanin kashi 14 cikin ɗari na masu kamuwa da COVID-19 suna ci gaba zuwa wani yanayi mai tsanani da ke buƙatar asibiti, sauran kashi 6 cikin ɗari suna cikin mawuyacin hali, inda ake buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani.
Yawan mutuwar marasa lafiya da ke cikin asibiti da COVID-19 ya kai kusan kashi 4%.
Wannan binciken ya yi nazarin yanayin cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa ta Tarayyar Turai (EU) / Yankin Tattalin Arzikin Turai (EEA) da Burtaniya kuma ya kwatanta su da yanayin lardin Hubei na China.
Mun kuma kwatanta adadin masu kamuwa da COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Birtaniya da na Italiya daga 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Birtaniya
Bayan barkewar cutar a China, COVID-19 ta yadu zuwa wasu ƙasashe, kuma a halin yanzu a sauran duniya annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba daidai da yadda ta faru a China.
A ranar 11 ga Maris, 2020, Darakta Janar na Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ya ayyana cutar COVID-19 a matsayin annoba.
A cikin mujallar Eurosurveillance ta 5 ga Maris, 2020, Mista Spiteri da abokan aikinsa sun ba da rahoton farkon tabbatar da cutar COVID-19 a Turai waɗanda suka cika ƙa'idodin WHO don gano cutar.
An samu mutum uku da suka kamu da cutar a Faransa a ranar 24 ga watan Janairun 2020  dukansu sun dawo daga birnin Wuhan na lardin Hubei na kasar Sin.
A ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, an gano cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin dukkan ƙasashe 30 na EU/EEA da Burtaniya, tare da a cikin lokacin daga 31 ga Disamba, 2019 zuwa wannan ranar an sami kamuwa da cutar 39,768 da mutuwar 1,727, daga cikinsu akwai 17,750 daga cikinsu 1,441 da suka mutu a Italiya kadai.
Tabbatar da yawan adadin COVID-19 da yawan kamuwa da cutar
Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka ta Turai (ECDC) tana sabunta bayanai game da adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a kowace ƙasa a duniya a kowace rana da ƙarfe 8:00 na safe, daga kafofin hukuma kamar ma'aikatun kiwon lafiya na waɗannan ƙasashe, hukumomin kiwon lafiya na ƙasa da na yanki da WHO.
Ana amfani da wannan bayanan don nazarin yanayin yaduwar COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da UK da kuma kwatanta su da bayanan Italiya.
An ƙididdige yawan adadin masu cutar COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 tare da la'akari da yanayin COVID-19 na yau da kullun a kowace ƙasa ta EU / EEA da Burtaniya daga 1 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Mun kuma nuna adadin adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a kowace ƙasa da karfe 8:00 na ranar 15 ga Maris, 2020, idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya daga ranar 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Yanayin COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya
Hanyoyin ci gaban cututtukan COVID-19 a cikin kwanaki 14 a cikin EU / EEA da Burtaniya gabaɗaya sun yi daidai da abubuwan da aka lura a lardin Hubei na China (Fig. 1).
Yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya gabaɗaya ya fara ƙaruwa a kusan 21 ga Fabrairu, kuma a ranar 28 ga Fabrairu, 2020 an sami tsalle-tsalle a cikin wannan adadin (ƙarin bayani).
Wannan ya kasance saboda yawan karuwar adadin masu kamuwa da cutar a Italiya, amma duk sauran ƙasashen EU/EEA da Burtaniya sun lura da irin wannan yanayin karuwar yawan kamuwa da COVID-19 (ƙarin bayani).
Hoto na 2 ya nuna adadin mutanen da suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin EU/EEA da Birtaniya idan aka kwatanta da adadin da aka samu a Italiya a tsakanin 31 ga Janairu zuwa 15 ga Maris, 2020.
Bisa ga wannan, yawan adadin da aka riga aka samu a ranar 15 ga Maris da karfe 8:00 na dare a wasu ƙasashe 15 na EU/EEA da kuma Burtaniya, ya yi daidai da adadin da aka samu a Italiya makonni uku da suka gabata.
Sakamakon bincikenmu ya nuna cewa an samu karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 a EU/EEA da Birtaniya.
Hanyoyin da ake lura da su na yawan kamuwa da cutar COVID-19 sun nuna cewa annobar tana ci gaba da sauri a duk ƙasashe.
Kuma wannan duk da cewa akwai matakai daban-daban a ƙasashe daban-daban, da bambance-bambance a matakan da hukumomin kiwon lafiyar jama'a na ƙasa ke ɗauka, kuma wataƙila akwai ma'auni daban-daban na ganewar cutar da kuma ƙa'idodin zaɓin marasa lafiya don gwajin COVID-19, gami da gwajin "sakewa".
A farkon watan Maris na 2020, likitoci a yankunan da cutar ta shafa na Italiya sun ba da rahoton cewa kusan kashi 10 cikin ɗari na marasa lafiya da ke fama da COVID-19 suna buƙatar kulawa mai tsanani, kuma kafofin watsa labarai sun ce asibitoci da sassan kulawa mai tsanani a waɗannan yankuna sun cika sosai.
A halin yanzu, ana samun bayanai game da shigar da marasa lafiya da COVID-19 asibitoci da (ko) sassan kulawa mai tsanani a cikin EU / EEA kawai game da kashi 6 cikin ɗari da kashi 1 cikin ɗari na shari'o'in daidai (ba a ba da bayanai ba).
Amma, ana bukatar a riƙa tattara irin wannan bayanan a kai a kai don a ci gaba da lura da yawan masu cutar da kuma yawan mutanen da suka mutu.
A cewar wani bincike da aka gudanar a shekara ta 2010 zuwa 2011, an samu raguwar gadaje a dakunan jinya da kuma dakunan kula da marasa lafiya a Turai: daga gado 29.2 a Jamus zuwa gadaje 4.2 a kowace mutum 100,000 a Portugal.
Wannan yana nufin cewa wasu ƙasashe suna da ƙarin ko ƙasa da albarkatu fiye da Italiya (gado 12.5 a cikin ICU da ICU a kowace mazauna 100,000 a 2010-2011).
Rahoton ECDC na shida da aka sabunta game da sakamakon kimanta haɗarin COVID-19 ya ba da yanayin samfurin tsarin kiwon lafiya tare da kimantawa game da asibiti na COVID-19 a kowace EU / EEA da Burtaniya, lokacin da haɗarin rashin gadaje a cikin sassan kulawa mai tsanani ya wuce 90%.
Tun da yake a halin yanzu an rarraba masu kamuwa da cutar zuwa wasu yankuna na EU/EEA da UK, kuma asibitoci da dakunan jinya na musamman suna kula da yawan jama'a a cikin wani yanki, ana ba da shawarar bayar da bayanai game da cututtuka da adadin gadaje a dakunan jinya a matakin 2 na Ƙididdigar Ƙasa don dalilai na kididdiga (NUTS-2).
Kwarewar Italiya da kuma abubuwan da ke faruwa a wasu ƙasashe sun nuna cewa annobar COVID-19 tana ci gaba da sauri a cikin EU/EEA da Burtaniya.
Saboda haka, ƙasashe, asibitoci da dakunan jinya na musamman dole ne su kasance a shirye don yanayin kamuwa da SARS-CoV-2 na tuntuɓar wanda ba ya raguwa na dogon lokaci, da kuma ƙaruwar yawan marasa lafiya da COVID-19 da ke buƙatar kulawa ta likita, musamman kulawa mai tsanani, kamar yadda ake gani a yankunan da ke fama da cutar a Italiya.
Kamar yadda rahoton ECDC na baya-bayan nan ya nuna, gaggawa, tsinkaye da kuma daidaitawa yana da mahimmanci don hana yaduwar SARS-COV-2 tare da sauyawa daga hanawa zuwa rage tasirin, saboda yawan ƙwayoyin cuta da aka yi hasashen zai iya haifar da ƙarancin lokaci ga masu yanke shawara da asibitoci don tsarawa, ɗauka da daidaitawa idan ba a ɗauki irin waɗannan matakan ba.
Rahoton da aka bayar ya kuma nuna matakan da za a dauka don rage radadin annobar.
Kasashe suna da ɗan gajeren lokaci don ƙara ƙarfin ƙoƙarce-ƙoƙarcen su don rage yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 da rage nauyin da ke kan tsarin kiwon lafiyarsu.
Idan ba a yi hakan ba, a cikin kwanaki ko makonni masu zuwa, za a sami ƙarin marasa lafiya da ke bukatar jinya a wasu ƙasashen Tarayyar Turai da kuma yankin da ake kira EEA.
Cutar coronavirus ta 2019 (COVID-19), wadda cutar coronavirus ta haifar da mummunan cututtukan numfashi (SARS) nau'in 2 (SARS-CoV-2), ta zama bala'i ga ɗan adam: a halin yanzu mutane sama da 3 000 sun mutu a China da sauran ƙasashen duniya, kuma adadin masu kamuwa da cutar ya wuce 80,000.
Kamar kwayar cutar SARS-CoV da ta haifar da ciwon numfashi mai tsanani a cikin dubban mutane a 2003, SARS-CoV-2 na iya zama daga bera kuma yana haifar da alamun bayyanar cututtuka iri ɗaya ta amfani da irin wannan hanyar.
Ko da yake COVID-19 ba ta da tsanani sosai kuma ba ta mutuwa sosai kamar SARS, amma tana da saurin kamuwa da cuta kuma tana shafar tsofaffi fiye da matasa, da maza fiye da mata.
