Za mu tattauna game da cututtuka da kuma yadda za a magance su.
Ko da yake ba a amsa tambayoyi da yawa ba, muna fatan wannan binciken zai taimaka mana mu fahimci wannan muguwar cuta kuma mu kawar da ita.
Bikin bazara (Sabuwar Shekarar kasar Sin), wanda ya zo ranar 25 ga Janairu, ya zama abin da ba a taɓa mantawa da shi ba ga duk Sinawa, waɗanda saboda barkewar sabon kamuwa da cutar kwayar cutar, an bukaci su zauna a gida a duk lokacin bikin da kuma makonni da yawa bayan haka.
Ganin irin kamanceceniyar da ke tsakanin cutar coronavirus (CoV) da ta haifar da cutar SARS a 2003, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya (WHO) ta sanya wa wannan kwayar cutar sunan SARS-CoV-2 a ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, 2020, kuma cutar da ke tattare da ita  cutar coronavirus 19 (COVID-19).
An fara annobar ne a birnin Wuhan na kasar Sin kuma ta bazu cikin sauri a fadin kasar, daga nan kuma zuwa kusan wasu kasashe 50 na duniya.
A ranar 2 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da sama da mutane 80,000 da suka kamu da cutar COVID-19, sama da mutane 40,000 sun warke, sama da mutane 3,000 sun mutu.
WHO ta yi gargadin cewa COVID-19 "maƙiyi na farko ga al'umma" ne kuma yana iya zama mafi haɗari fiye da ta'addanci.
A cewar PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), a cikin ƙasa da watanni biyu, an buga labarai sama da 200 game da COVID-19, gami da labarai game da ilimin ƙwayoyin cuta, cututtukan cututtuka, ilimin cututtuka, ganewar asali da magani, tun daga rahoton farko na 7 ga Janairu, 2020, wanda ya gano jerin ƙwayoyin cuta da aka ware daga yawancin marasa lafiya.
Wannan bita yana ƙoƙari ne na taƙaita sakamakon bincike a cikin sabon yanki mai tasowa.
Idan za mu iya, za mu gwada COVID-19 da SARS da kuma wata cutar da ke haifar da cutar coronavirus  cutar sankarar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya (MERS) wanda ya ɓarke a 2012.
