Saboda haka, cutar COVID-19 ta yanzu ita ce kamuwa da cutar coronavirus ta uku a tarihin ɗan adam.
Kamar yadda aka nuna a hoto na 1.1, rahoton farko game da tarin fuka-fukan cutar sankarar bargo ya fara zuwa Hukumar Lafiya ta Kasa ta kasar Sin daga Wuhan a ranar 31 ga Disamba, 2019.
Bayan kwana bakwai, an saki tsarin kwayoyin cutar.
A ranar 15 ga Janairun 2020, an sami mutuwar mutum na farko a Wuhan.
A wannan lokacin, annobar ta bazu cikin sauri zuwa garuruwa da larduna da ƙasashe makwabta.
A ranar 20 ga Janairu, an gano cewa ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya sun kamu da cutar, wanda ya ba da damar yin tunanin yiwuwar yaduwar cutar daga mutum zuwa mutum.
A ranar 23 ga Janairu, an kafa dokar hana fita a birnin Wuhan, kuma an dakatar da zirga-zirgar jama'a.
A ranar 24 ga watan Janairu, binciken farko na cutar ya nuna cewa 21 daga cikin marasa lafiya 41 da ke da cutar coronavirus sun kasance suna da alaƙa kai tsaye da kasuwar abincin teku a Wuhan, wanda aka ɗauka cewa asalin cutar daga dabba da ba a sani ba.
A ranar 30 ga watan Janairu, Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta bayyana cewa annobar korona ta zama gaggawa a fannin kiwon lafiyar jama'a.
A lokacin da aka shirya wannan rahoto, cutar ta yadu a duk faɗin Sin kuma ta riga ta shiga wasu ƙasashe 50 a duniya (hoto (hoto 2).2).
Idan aka yi la'akari da yadda lamarin ke ci gaba, har yanzu ba a san iyakar yadda cutar za ta kai ga barkewa ba.
A ranar 11 ga Fabrairun 2020, sakamakon binciken asibiti na cibiyoyi da yawa wanda ya shafi marasa lafiya 8,866, gami da marasa lafiya 4,021 da aka tabbatar da COVID-19, ya gabatar da sabon yanayin cutar (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
Ko da yake mutane masu shekaru daban-daban suna da saurin kamuwa da cutar SARS-CoV-2, amma yawanci mutane masu shekaru 30 zuwa 65 ne ke kamuwa da cutar.
