A ranar 14 ga Fabrairun 2020, an sami sama da mutane 2,500 da ke fama da cutar sankarar numfashi ta Gabas ta Tsakiya tare da yawan mace-mace (34.4%), saboda haka MERS-CoV ana ɗaukarsa ɗayan ƙwayoyin cuta masu saurin mutuwa da aka sani.
A tsakiyar zuwa ƙarshen watan Disamba na 2019, an gano tarin marasa lafiya da cutar huhu a Wuhan, lardin Hubei na ƙasar Sin, wanda yanzu, idan aka duba baya, ana danganta shi da kamuwa da cutar coronavirus mai tsanani mai tsanani na 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya ta sanar da cewa barkewar cutar sankara ta kasa da SARS-CoV-2 ke haifarwa, ta zama gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a a duniya, kuma an kira cutar coronavirus infection 19 (COVID-19).
A ranar 3 ga Maris, 2020, an tabbatar da mutane 90,053 a duniya, tare da mutuwar kusan kashi 3,4%.
Ya kamata a lura cewa yawan mutuwar a lardin Hubei na kasar Sin ya kai kashi 4.2 cikin dari, kuma a waje da shi ya kai kashi 1.2 cikin dari.
SARS-CoV-2, kamar SARS da MERS, yana haifar da mummunar kamuwa da cuta ta numfashi, wanda ke haifar da zazzabi, tari da rashin numfashi.
Wasu marasa lafiya suna fama da zazzabi.
Ciwon huhu yana da tsanani sosai kuma yana iya saurin saurin ciwo.
Duk da kamanceceniya tsakanin SARS-CoV da SARS-CoV-2, la'akari da babban daidaiton jerin nucleotide (82%), waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta duk da haka suna samar da rassa daban-daban na itacen phylogenetic.
SARS-CoV-2 a bayyane yake ba shi da cutar amma yana da damar watsawa fiye da SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
An samu wasu mutane da ba su nuna alamun cutar SARS-CoV-2 ba, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa cutar tana iya yaduwa cikin sauri a duniya.
Idan aka kwatanta SARS-CoV-2 da sauran kwayar cutar coronavirus guda shida, za a ga muhimman kamanceceniya da bambance-bambance.
Na farko, cututtukan da ke kama da na mutum suna da irin wannan lokacin da suke ci gaba da yaduwa.
A wannan yanayin, SARS-CoV-2 yana nuna irin yanayin da sauran cututtukan coronavirus guda shida na ɗan adam.
Na biyu, a cikin yanayin cutar COVID-19, cutar SARS-CoV tana tsakanin cutar coronavirus guda huɗu da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti (watau HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 da HCoV-NL63).
A gefe guda, bayyanar cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta yi kama da na kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti, gami da bayyanar cututtuka marasa ƙayyadaddun, alamu masu sauƙi ko ma babu alamomi.
A gefe guda kuma, kamar yadda yake da SARS-CoV, za a iya rarrabe ƙananan ƙananan masu cutar COVID-19, ko da yake ƙimar ta ɗan ƙasa.
Na uku, akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa game da watsa SARS-CoV-2 da ke faruwa a cikin kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti da kuma SARS-CoV.
A gefe guda, yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 tana da girma kamar na coronavirus na mutum, wanda ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti.
A gefe guda, har yanzu ba a tabbatar da ko yaduwar SARS-CoV-2 ta ragu ba tare da kowane sauyawar cutar (watau kamuwa da kowane mutum na gaba), kamar yadda yake a cikin SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV.
A ƙarshe, kamar sauran cututtukan coronavirus na mutum da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti, ana iya gano SARS-CoV-2 a cikin kayan ƙwari.
Har yanzu ba mu san ko hanyar SARS-CoV-2 ta baki da na ƙwanƙwasa ba tana da mahimmanci (aƙalla a wasu yanayi) kamar yadda yake a cikin SARS-CoV.
Wani abin sha'awa musamman shi ne yiwuwar SARS-CoV-2 na yanayi, wanda ya shafi kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum, wanda ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti.
Koyaya, ci gaban cutar COVID-19 mai gudana zai dogara ne akan halaye na SARS-CoV-2, gami da watsawa, cutarwa da ci gaba da yaduwa bayan wucewa ta hanyar mutane.
Dukkanin kwayar cutar coronavirus guda huɗu da ke haifar da kamuwa da cuta a waje da asibiti tare da alamun rashin lafiya sun dace da mutane.
A wani ɓangaren kuma, wataƙila mutane sun saba da waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta huɗu na ɗan adam.
A wasu kalmomi, duka biyun za a iya cewa su ne kawai waɗanda suka tsira daga annobar coronavirus na ɗan adam a baya.
Kwayar cutar korona ta mutum da ke haifar da mummunan cuta a cikin mutane da kuma mutanen da cutar korona ta haifar da mummunan cuta a cikin su ba su tsira ba.
Don hakan ya faru, kwayar cutar coronavirus ta mutum dole ne ta ninka a jikin mutum sosai don samun juyin halittar da za ta iya magance abubuwan da ke hana mai ɗaukar ta.
A wannan ma'anar, idan cutar SARS-CoV-2 ta ci gaba da ci gaba da yawa kuma mutane da yawa sun kamu da ita, to, za a iya samun damar kamuwa da cutar ga mutane.
Idan ya daidaita da kyau, zai yi wuya a hana yaduwar cutar tsakanin mutane ta hanyar keɓewa ko wasu matakan kula da cututtuka.
A cikin shekaru da yawa, mutane da yawa sun kamu da cutar korona guda huɗu da ke haifar da sanyi a cikin marasa lafiya.
Waɗannan ƙwayoyin cuta ba sa bukatar dabba mai riƙe da su.
Kwayoyin cutar SARS-CoV da MERS-CoV ba su dace da mutane sosai ba kuma ba za a iya ci gaba da yaduwar su tsakanin mutane ba.
Suna bukatar su ci gaba da rayuwa da kuma haifuwa a cikin wuraren da suke zama, kuma su nemi zarafin shiga cikin mutane masu saurin kamuwa da cutar, wataƙila ta hanyar ɗaya ko fiye da masu ɗauke da cutar ko masu ƙarfafawa.
SARS-CoV-2 yana da halaye kamar SARS-CoV/MERS-CoV da kuma ƙwayoyin cuta huɗu na HCoV.
Yana da sauƙin yaduwa kamar HCoVs da ba sa zuwa asibiti, aƙalla a yanzu.
Amma ya fi HCoVs na waje cutarwa kuma ba ya cutar da SARS-CoV ko MERS-CoV.
Za mu ga ko zai iya zama mai amfani sosai ga mutane kuma ya yi tafiya a cikin yanayin da ba shi da tanki ko kuma ya yi tafiya tare da dabba mai ɗaukarwa.
Kafin mu tattauna asalin dabbobi na HCoVs, zai zama da amfani mu tattauna ma'anoni da halaye na juyin halitta, na halitta, na tsaka-tsaki, masu haɓaka da masu riƙe da HCoVs.
Dabbobi suna ɗaukar HCoV ta hanyar juyin halitta idan sun ɗauki dangi na kusa da ke da daidaituwa a matakin jerin nucleotides.
Kwayar cutar ta asali tana da kyau kuma ba ta haifar da cututtuka a cikin wannan mai ɗaukar hoto.
Hakazalika, mai ɗaukar hoto yana ɗaukar HCoV a cikin dogon lokaci.
A cikin duka biyun, masu ɗaukar hoto sun kamu da cutar ta hanyar halitta kuma suna ɗaukar hoto na HCoV ko kuma kwayar cutar mahaifa.
Akasin haka, idan HCoV ya kamu da cutar ne kawai a cikin mai ɗaukar hoto kafin ko a lokacin da aka kawo shi ga ɗan adam, ba ya dace da sabon mai ɗaukar hoto kuma sau da yawa yana haifar da cuta.
Wannan mai ɗaukar hoto na iya zama tushen cutar ta mutum kuma ya zama mai ɗaukar hoto mai haɓaka, yana ba da damar kwayar cutar ta ninka da sauri, sannan ya watsa ta ga mutane, yana ƙara yawan kamuwa da mutane.
HCoV na iya ɗaukar kamuwa da cuta ta hanyar kamuwa da cuta idan ba zai iya jurewa watsawa a cikin mai ɗaukarwa ba.
Akasin haka, ƙwayoyin HCoVs na iya daidaitawa da mai ɗaukar hoto na tsakiya har ma da kafa ƙarancin lokaci.
A wannan yanayin, mai ɗaukarwa na tsakiya ya zama mai ɗaukar ruwa na halitta.
Bayanan cututtuka sun nuna cewa mai cutar SARS ba shi da dangantaka da dabbobi masu farauta.
