William Schaffner, wani ma'aikaci a Jami'ar Vanderbilt ya ce: "Ba na tsammanin wannan cutar za ta taɓa ɓacewa gaba ɗaya, domin tana da saukin yaduwa kuma tana iya zama cuta ta yanayi, tana ɓarkewa kowace shekara".
