Alamomin COVID-19 na iya zama marasa ƙayyadaddun, kuma wasu mutane masu kamuwa da cutar na iya ɗaukar cutar ba tare da alamomi ba.
Alamun biyu da suka fi yawa sune zazzabi (88%) da tari mai bushe (68%).
Alamomin da ba a saba gani ba sun haɗa da gajiya, ƙwayoyin cuta a cikin hanyoyin numfashi (mucous), rashin wari, numfashi, ciwo a cikin tsokoki da haɗin gwiwa, ciwon makogwaro, ciwon kai, rawar jiki, amai, zubar da jini, zawo ko cyanosis.
Cibiyoyin Kula da Cututtuka da Cututtuka na Amurka (CDC) sun lissafa alamun gaggawa kamar wahalar numfashi, ciwo mai ɗorewa ko jin matsi a kirji, kwatsam rashin fahimta, wahalar farkawa da launin shuɗi na fuska ko lebe. Idan akwai waɗannan alamun ya kamata a nemi taimakon likita nan da nan. Ci gaba da cutar na iya haifar da ciwon huhu mai tsanani, ciwon damuwa na numfashi mai tsanani, sepsis, septic shock da mutuwa.
