A matakin kwayoyin halitta, ya kasance daidai da sauran samfuran kwayar cutar coronavirus na bat (BatCov RaTG13) da kashi 96%.
A watan Fabrairun 2020, masu binciken kasar Sin sun gano cewa akwai bambanci guda daya kawai a cikin amino acid na wasu sassan tsarin kwayoyin halittar kwayar cutar pangolin da na mutum.
Kwatanta kwayoyin halittar mutum da kwayoyin halitta ya nuna cewa mafi yawan kamanceceniya (92%) tsakanin kwayar cutar ta coronavirus da SARS-CoV-2 amma wannan bai isa ya tabbatar da cewa pangolins sune masu karɓar kwayar cutar ba.
Ana iya gano kamuwa da cutar ta hanyar alamomi, amma a ƙarshe ana iya tabbatar da hakan ta hanyar nazarin ƙwayar cuta ta hanyar ƙwayar cuta ta hanyar ƙwayar cuta ko ta hanyar kwamfuta.
Sakamakon binciken da ya kwatanta PCR da CT da aka yi amfani da su a Wuhan ya nuna cewa CT ya fi PCR hankali sosai, ko da yake ba shi da ƙayyadaddun bayani, saboda yawancin ayyukansa na gani sun dace da sauran cututtukan huhu da kuma cututtuka.
Tun daga watan Maris na 2020, Kwalejin Radiology ta Amurka ta ba da shawarar kada a yi amfani da CT don tantancewa ko a matsayin hanyar gwaji ta farko don gano COVID-19.
