Likitoci takwas daga cikin wadannan likitocin, ciki har da Li Wenliang, 'yan sanda sun yi musu gargadi game da alhakin yada jita-jita, kuma likitan, Ai Feng, ya sami tsawatawa daga shugabanninsa saboda tayar da firgici.
