Duk manyan wasannin motsa jiki, gami da wasannin kwallon kafa na A, ya kamata a rufe su har zuwa Afrilu, amma a ranar 9 ga Maris an jinkirta duk wasannin motsa jiki aƙalla wata ɗaya.
