A tsakiyar Janairu 2020, mujallar Travel Medicine ta buga nazarin tsarin tafiye-tafiyen jirgin sama, wanda aka yi amfani da shi don zana taswira da hasashen yanayin yaduwar cutar.
Bisa ga bayanan kungiyar sufurin jiragen sama ta duniya a shekarar 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo da Taipei sun karbi mafi yawan matafiya daga Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney da Melbourne ma sun kasance sanannun wuraren da masu yawon bude ido ke zuwa.
Daga cikin manyan wuraren shakatawa 20, Bali an kira shi mafi ƙarancin shirye-shiryen barkewar cutar, yayin da biranen Ostiraliya aka ɗauka mafi shirye. A ranar 7 ga Fabrairu, Ostiraliya ta ɗauki shirin ta na gaggawa game da sabon coronavirus (COVID-19).
A wannan yanayin, an ce akwai abubuwa da yawa da za a koya game da COVID-19, kuma cewa Ostiraliya za ta ba da hankali sosai ga kula da kan iyakoki da sadarwa a cikin yanayin barazanar.
