Sakamakon ingantattun matakan killacewa da aka sanya a bangaren sufuri na jama'a a Wuhan da Hubei, wasu kasashe sun shirya kwashe 'yan kasarsu da ma'aikatan diflomasiyya daga yankin, galibi ta hanyar jiragen sama na kasashensu, wanda hukumomin kasar Sin suka ba da izinin.
Kasashen Kanada, Amurka, Japan, Indiya, Sri Lanka, Ostiraliya, Faransa, Argentina, Jamus da Thailand sun kasance cikin na farko da suka shirya fitar da 'yan kasarsu.
