A ranar 11 ga Fabrairu, wani jirgin sama tare da 'yan Kanada 185 da aka fitar daga Wuhan ya sauka a CFB Trenton.
A ranar 3 da 4 ga watan Fabrairu, hukumomin Australia sun kwashe 'yan kasar 277 kuma suka sanya su a cibiyar zama na wucin gadi a tsibirin Kirsimeti, wanda aka sake fasalin shi zuwa cibiyar killacewa, inda suka zauna har tsawon kwanaki 14.
A ranar 5 ga Fabrairu, jirgin sama na New Zealand ya isa Auckland; fasinjojinsa (ciki har da wasu daga Ostiraliya da yankin Asiya da Fasifik) an sanya su cikin keɓewa a sansanin sojan ruwa a Vangaparoa, arewacin Auckland.
A ranar 15 ga Fabrairu, Amurka ta sanar da cewa za ta kwashe 'yan ƙasar Amurka da ke cikin jirgin ruwan Diamond Princess.
A ranar 21 ga Fabrairu, jirgin sama mai dauke da fasinjojin Kanada 129 da aka kwashe daga "Diamond Princess" ya sauka a Trenton, Ontario.
A farkon watan Maris, gwamnatin Indiya ta fara kwashe 'yan kasar ta daga Iran. A ranar 14 ga Maris, jirgin saman kamfanin jirgin sama na South African Airways, wanda gwamnatin Afirka ta Kudu ta yi haya, ya tashi tare da' yan Afirka ta Kudu 112 a cikin jirgin.
An yi wa fasinjojin gwajin lafiya kafin tashi, kuma an bar 'yan Afirka ta Kudu hudu da ke da alamun cutar coronavirus a China don rage haɗarin.
An kwashe 'yan Afirka ta Kudu ne kawai da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus.
An yi gwajin daga dukkan 'yan Afirka ta Kudu, gami da ma'aikatan jirgin sama, matukan jirgi, ma'aikatan otal,' yan sanda da sojoji da ke cikin aikin agaji, kuma a matsayin kariya, duk sun kasance a karkashin kulawa da keɓewa na kwanaki 14 a The Ranch Resort.
A ranar 20 ga watan Maris, Amurka ta fara janye dakarunta daga Iraki saboda annobar.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen China ta sanar da cewa kasashe 21 (ciki har da Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad da Tobago, Masar da Iran) sun tura taimakon su zuwa kasar Sin.
Wasu daliban kasar Sin da ke karatu a jami'o'in Amurka sun hada kai don tarawa da kuma tura taimako zuwa yankunan da cutar ta shafa na kasar Sin, tare da wani rukuni daga Chicago da aka ruwaito sun aika da kayan aikin N95 50,000 zuwa asibitocin lardin Hubei a ranar 30 ga Janairu.
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, Bill da Melinda Gates sun sanar da bayar da gudummawar dala miliyan 100 ga Hukumar Lafiya ta Duniya don tallafawa samar da allurar rigakafi da maganin cutar coronavirus, da kuma kare mutanen Afirka da Kudancin Asiya daga barazanar cutar.
Interaksyon ta ruwaito cewa a ranar 6 ga watan Fabrairu, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da gudummawar masks 200,000 ga kasar Philippines bayan da Sanata Richard Gordon ya aika da masks miliyan 3.16 zuwa Wuhan.
A ranar 19 ga watan Fabrairu, kungiyar agaji ta Singapore ta sanar da cewa za ta aika da tallafin da ya kai dala miliyan 2.26 ga kasar Sin.
Japan ta kuma ba da gudummawar abin rufe fuska miliyan daya, Turkiyya ta aika da kayan aikin likita zuwa Wuhan, Rasha  sama da tan 13 na magunguna, Malaysia ta sanar da bayar da gudummawar safar hannu miliyan 18, Jamus ta aika da kayan aikin likita daban-daban, gami da kayan kariya 10,000, Amurka ta ba da gudummawar tan 17.8 na magunguna, tare da yin alkawarin ba da dala miliyan 100 a matsayin tallafin kuɗi ga ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa. Bayan halin da ake ciki a China ya daidaita, ƙasar ta kuma aika da taimako ga sauran ƙasashen da cutar ta shafa.
A watan Maris, China, Cuba da Rasha sun tura magunguna da masana zuwa Italiya don taimakawa mutane su magance cutar coronavirus.
Wani dan kasuwa mai suna Jack Ma ya aika wa Kungiyar Tarayyar Afirka, Addis Ababa, Habasha, da kayan gwaji miliyan 1.1, da abin rufe fuska miliyan 6, da kuma riguna 60,000 don kungiyar ta rarraba su a kasashe mambobinta.
Daga baya kuma ya aika da kayan gwaji 5,000, abin rufe fuska 100,000 da na'urorin shan magani guda biyar zuwa Panama.
Ma ya kuma ba da gudummawar magunguna ga Kanada. Netherlands, Spain, Turkey, Georgia da Jamhuriyar Czech sun nuna damuwa game da abin rufe fuska da kayan gwaji na kasar Sin.
Alal misali, Spain ta dawo da kayan gwajin cutar korona na kasar Sin 58,000 da ke da daidaito na kashi 30 cikin dari, kuma Netherlands ta dawo da abin rufe fuska na kasar Sin 600,000 da suka lalace.
Belgium ta kuma dawo da abin rufe fuska 100,000 da ba za a iya amfani da su ba: ana zaton an yi su ne a China, amma daga baya an gano cewa sun fito ne daga Colombia.
A wani bangare kuma, an yi maraba da taimakon da kasar Sin ta bayar a wasu sassan Latin Amurka da Afirka.
Hukumar lafiya ta duniya ta yaba wa kokarin da hukumomin kasar Sin ke yi na dakile yaduwar cutar.
Hukumar ta WHO ta lura da bambance-bambance tsakanin barkewar cutar sankarar bargo a shekarar 2002-2004, inda aka zargi hukumomin kasar Sin da boye bayanai, wanda ake zargin yana hana rigakafin cutar da kuma hana yaduwarta, da kuma rikicin yanzu, inda gwamnatin tsakiya ke ba da cikakken bayani game da yanayin don kauce wa firgici a jajibirin Sabuwar Shekarar Sin.
A ranar 23 ga watan Janairu, a mayar da martani ga matakin da hukumomin tsakiya suka dauka na hana zirga-zirgar ababen hawa a Wuhan, wakilin WHO, Goden Galea ya ce, ko da yake ba WHO ce ta ba da shawarar wannan matakin ba, amma kuma "babban tabbaci ne na cika alƙawarin da aka ɗauka na hana barkewar cutar a inda ta fi yaduwa", kuma ya kira ta "ba tare da misali ba a tarihin kiwon lafiyar jama'a". A ranar 30 ga Janairu, bayan da aka tabbatar da cewa kamuwa da cutar na iya yaduwa daga mutum zuwa mutum a wajen China da kuma karuwar masu kamuwa da cutar a wasu ƙasashe, WHO ta ayyana gaggawa ta kiwon lafiyar jama'a mai ma'ana ta duniya (PHEIC); wannan shine karo na shida tun daga 2009 da aka fara amfani da irin wannan matakin a lokacin annobar mura ta duniya.
Darakta Janar na WHO, Mr Tedros Adhanom ya ce sanarwar PHEIC ta shafi hadarin yaduwar cutar a duniya, musamman a kasashe masu karamin karfi da matsakaitan kudade da ba su da ingantaccen tsarin kiwon lafiya.
Da yake magana game da takunkumin tafiye-tafiye, Mista Tedros ya ce "babu wani dalili da zai sa a dauki matakan da za su hana zirga-zirgar kasa da kasa da cinikayya" kuma "WHO ba ta bayar da shawarar hana zirga-zirga da cinikayya".
A ranar 5 ga watan Fabrairu, WHO ta nemi al'ummar duniya da su ba da dala miliyan 675 don samar da shirye-shiryen da za a yi a ƙasashe masu karamin kuɗi, ta bayyana bukatar ba da taimako na gaggawa ga ƙasashen da ba su da tsarin gano mutanen da ke da cutar, duk da cewa cutar ba ta kai waɗannan ƙasashe ba tukuna.
Mista Tedros ya kuma ce "mai nuna shirye-shiryenmu" shine yadda muka shirya wa cutar a inda ta fi rauni, kuma ya bukaci al'ummar duniya su "yi zabi tsakanin saka hannun jari a yau ko biyan bashin nan gaba". A wani taron manema labarai da WHO ta yi a ranar 11 ga watan Fabrairu, ta sanya wa cutar sunan "COVID-19".
A wannan rana, Tedros ya ce Sakatare Janar na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya Antonio Guterres ya amince da samar da "dukan tsarin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don amsa matsalar".
Sakamakon haka, an kafa kungiyar kula da rikicin Majalisar Dinkin Duniya don daidaita dukkan martani na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya; wadannan matakan, in ji WHO, za su ba da damar "mai da hankali kan amsawa a fannin kiwon lafiya, yayin da sauran hukumomi za su iya amfani da kwarewarsu don magance barkewar cutar a cikin yanayin zamantakewar da tattalin arziki".
