Aikace-aikacen COVID-19 aikace-aikacen software ne na wayar hannu da aka tsara don taimakawa a cikin binciken annoba a cikin annobar cutar coronavirus ta 2019-20, wato, gano mutanen da zasu iya tuntuɓar mutum mai cutar.
A wasu yankuna, an samar da aikace-aikace da yawa da aka amince da su a hukumance.
An yi amfani da wasu aikace-aikace don saka idanu kan lambobin sadarwa.
Wannan ya haifar da muhawara game da matsalolin sirri, musamman game da tsarin da ke dogara da bin diddigin wurin da masu amfani da aikace-aikacen suke.
Zaɓuɓɓuka masu laushi a wannan batun sun haɗa da amfani da siginar Bluetooth don yin rajistar kusanci mai amfani da wasu wayoyin hannu.
A ranar 10 ga Afrilu, 2020, Google da Apple sun ba da sanarwar cewa za su haɗa haɗin gwiwa don haɗa haɗin ayyukan tallafi na irin waɗannan aikace-aikacen da ke da tushen Bluetooth kai tsaye cikin tsarin aiki na Android da iOS.
A China, gwamnati tare da Alipay sun ƙaddamar da wata manhaja da ke ba 'yan ƙasa damar bincika ko sun taɓa yin hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar COVID-19.
Ana amfani da shi a birane sama da 200 na kasar Sin, kuma a Singapore akwai wata manhaja da ake kira TraceTogether.
An samar da manhajar ne ta kamfanonin IT na cikin gida, kuma an bude ta kuma za a mika ta ga gwamnati.
Ma'aikatar Sadarwa da Fasaha da Ma'aikatar Lafiya sun haɗa kai don tsara manhajar.
A ranar 14 ga Afrilu, 2020, aikace-aikacen yana jiran rajista a cikin Google Play Store da Apple App Store.
A ranar 12 ga Afrilu, gwamnati ta ce aikace-aikacen bin diddigin lamba yana kan matakin karshe na ci gaba kuma zai kasance a shirye don turawa a cikin 'yan makonni.
Australia da New Zealand suna nazarin amfani da aikace-aikacen da ke da tushe a kan aikace-aikacen TraceTogether na Singapore da yarjejeniyar BlueTrace. Rasha tana da niyyar amfani da aikace-aikacen da ke da fasalin yanki wanda ke da niyyar  lura da cewa marasa lafiya da ke da cutar COVID-19 da ke zaune a Moscow ba su bar gidajensu.
Ross Anderson, Farfesa a Tsaro, Jami'ar Cambridge, ya nuna wasu matsalolin da za su iya faruwa tare da tsarin aikace-aikacen, ciki har da kuskure da kuma yiwuwar rashin amfani idan ƙananan mutane suna amfani da aikace-aikacen.
Dangane da damuwa game da yaduwar ɓatarwa ko aikace-aikacen cutar coronavirus, Apple ya iyakance jerin nau'ikan ƙungiyoyin da za su iya ba da aikace-aikacen da ke da alaƙa da cutar coronavirus a cikin App Store, suna haɗa da a'idar ko wasu ƙungiyoyi masu aminci a cikin wannan jerin.
Google da Amazon sun kafa irin wannan dokar.
Masu fafutukar kare sirrin jama'a sun nuna damuwa game da tasirin sa ido kan jama'a ta hanyar aikace-aikacen da ke da alaƙa da cutar coronavirus; musamman, an yi tambaya ko za a rushe tsarin sa ido da aka gina don magance cutar coronavirus lokacin da barazanar ta ɓace.
Ƙungiyar Amnesty International da wasu ƙungiyoyi sama da 100 sun wallafa wata sanarwa da ke kira da a rage irin wannan sa ido.
Kungiyoyin sun sanar da sharudda takwas da suke gabatar wa ayyukan gwamnati:
Dole ne a yi sa ido a kan abin da ya dace da doka, dole ne kuma daidai gwargwado.
fadada sa ido da lura dole ne ya kasance tare da sharhi game da iyakance lokacin aiki;
amfani da bayanai ya kamata ya kasance ne kawai don magance yaduwar COVID-19;
Dole ne a kare tsaro da rashin sani na bayanai kuma dole ne a ba da tabbacin wannan kariya;
digital lura kamata kauce wa sharudda nuna bambanci da kuma marginalization;
duk wani musayar bayanai tare da ɓangarorin uku dole ne a ƙayyade a matakin doka;
Dole ne a tabbatar da kariya daga cin zarafi, da kuma hakkin 'yan ƙasa na amsawa ga cin zarafi;
Ya kamata a samar da mahimman bayanai  daga dukkan masu ruwa da tsaki , ciki har da masana kiwon lafiya da wakilan kungiyoyi masu zaman kansu.
Google da Apple sun gabatar da shirin haɗin gwiwa don magance matsalar sa ido na dindindin, wanda ke nufin cire tsarin sa ido daga tsarin aiki na na'urorin su da zarar ba a buƙatar hakan.
A wasu ƙasashe, ana amfani da hanyar sadarwar wurin zama maimakon aikace-aikace, wanda ke kawar da buƙatar saukar da aikace-aikacen da kuma yiwuwar kauce wa sa ido.
An amince da bin sawun mutane a Isra'ila.
Hanyoyin sadarwa waɗanda ke da damar yin amfani da bayanan wuri na asali suna da manyan matsalolin sirri.
Duk da haka, ba duk tsarin da ke da sabobin tsakiya ba ne ya kamata su sami damar yin amfani da bayanan sirri game da wurin zama; an tsara wasu tsarin tare da tsare sirri wanda ke amfani da sabobin tsakiya kawai don sadarwa (duba sashe na ƙasa).
A Koriya ta Kudu, an yi amfani da tsarin da ba ya amfani da manhajar a matsayin tushen bin diddigin lambobin sadarwa.
Maimakon amfani da aikace-aikacen musamman, tsarin ya tattara bayanan sa ido daga tushe daban-daban, gami da bayanan sa ido na na'urorin hannu da ma'amalar katin, sannan ya haɗa su don ƙirƙirar sanarwa a cikin saƙonnin rubutu waɗanda aka aika wa mutanen da ke da yiwuwar kamuwa da cutar.
Gwamnati ba wai kawai ta yi amfani da wannan bayanin don faɗakar da 'yan ƙasa game da yiwuwar hulɗa da mutanen da ke da cutar ba, amma kuma ta ba da bayanin wurin zama ga jama'a, wanda ya yiwu saboda canje-canje masu mahimmanci a cikin dokokin kariya na bayanai da aka yi bayan barkewar MERS a wannan ƙasar.
Ana iya samun wannan bayanin ta hanyar wasu manhajoji da shafukan yanar gizo. Kasashe, ciki har da Jamus, suna la'akari da yiwuwar amfani da tsarin tsakiya da kuma tsarin tsare sirri.
A ranar 6 ga Afrilu, 2020 ba a sanar da cikakken bayani ba.
Binciken tuntuɓar sirri  tsari ne mai kyau wanda yawancin wallafe-wallafen bincike suka fara aƙalla 2013. Kamar yadda yake a ranar 7 ga Afrilu, 2020, sama da ƙungiyoyin masana goma suna aiki kan hanyoyin magance sirri kamar amfani da Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) don yin rajistar kusanci mai amfani da wasu wayoyin hannu.
Duk da haka, PEPP-PT samfurin haɗin gwiwar ne wanda ya haɗa da hanyoyin tsakiya da na rarraba, kuma ba yarjejeniya ɗaya ba.
Waɗannan hanyoyin sun tabbatar da cewa bayanan da aka gano ba su fita daga na'urar ba, amma duk abubuwan da aka yi a ciki.
The Privacy Group, MIT Media Lab tana haɓaka SafePaths, dandamali don tabbatar da sirrin sirri yayin tattarawa da amfani da bayanan wuri ko ƙetare hanya don bin diddigin yaduwar COVID-19.
Wannan aikin ya dogara ne akan binciken da aka bayar a cikin takaddar Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic (Aikace-aikacen ɓarna: yadda za a kiyaye sirrinka a lokacin annobar), wanda aka buga a watan Maris na 2020. Wani irin wannan aikin shine dandalin SafeTrace wanda Enigma MPC ya haɓaka, kamfanin da ke haɓaka fasahar tabbatar da sirrin, wanda kuma MIT Media Lab ta kafa shi.
SafeTrace yana amfani da ingantaccen fasahar kayan aiki wanda ke ba masu amfani damar musayar bayanan wuri da lafiyarsu tare da sauran masu amfani da jami'ai ba tare da yin haɗari ga sirrin bayanan ba.
